e widget rebuilt, a NEW cubit was created and `load()` was called, which would o
verwrite the user\'s input with the default URL.\n\n## Fix\n1. Changed DI regist
ration from `registerFactory` to `registerLazySingleton` for `DevToolsCubit`\n2.
Changed `DevToolsWrapper` to a StatefulWidget that gets the cubit once in `initS
tate()` and provides it via `BlocProvider.value`\n3. Added a widget test for "dr
awer close and reopen preserves saved url"\n4. Updated docs formatting\n\n## Rev
iew findings\n\n### Positive aspects\n- The fix addresses the root cause correct
